rules: :- permute(S, I1, J), permute(S, I2, J), I1 != I2.
holds(S, output_element(I), D) :- holds(S, input_digit, input_element(J), D), permute(S,J,I).
correct(S,I,I+1) :- holds(S, output_element(I), _), holds(S, output_element(I+1), _), permute(S,I1,I), permute(S,J1,I+1), I1<J1, holds(S, comparison, swap_input(I1,J1), not_swap).
correct(S,I,I+1) :- holds(S, output_element(I), _), holds(S, output_element(I+1), _), permute(S,I1,I), permute(S,J1,I+1), I1>J1, holds(S, comparison, swap_input(J1,I1), swap).
sorted(S) :- correct(S,0,1), correct(S,1,2), correct(S,2,3), correct(S,3,4), correct(S,4,5).
